                   &kp A      &kp A      &kp UP          &kp LS(NUMBER_0)  &kp LC(LA(NUMBER_7))    &kp LC(LA(NUMBER_0))  &kp NUMBER_7  &kp NUMBER_8  &kp NUMBER_9  &kp KP_PLUS
