&kp LC(LA(MINUS))  &kp PG_DN  &kp MINUS  &kp UNDERSCORE  &kp SLASH         &kp LS(NUMBER_8)        &kp LS(NUMBER_9)      &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &kp KP_DIVIDE
                                         &trans          &trans            &trans                  &kp LEFT_SHIFT        &mo 3         &kp KP_N0
            >;
